20Tesla%20prices%20are%20rising%20as%20the%20secondhand%20EV%20market%20booms%20following%20the%20end%20of%20the%20%247%2C500%20tax%20credit.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat's%20a%20relief%20for%20Tesla%20owners%2C%20who%20have%20seen%20resale%20prices%20plunge%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Model%20S%20and%20X%20saw%20the%20largest%20price%20hikes.%20Elon%20Musk%20said%20Tesla%20would%20discontinue%20them%20to%20build%20its%20Optimus%20robots.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20market%20for%20used%20Teslas%20is%20heating%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20booming%20secondhand%20EV%20market%20is%20pushing%20used%20Tesla%20prices%20up%20even%20as%20other%20electric%20vehicles%20get%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20price%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fused-tesla-prices-collapsing-owners-sell-up-elon-musk-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eused%20Tesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20climbed%204.3%25%20since%20the%20end%20of%20the%20%247%2C500%20tax%20credit%20for%20new%20electric%20vehicles%20in%20September%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20used%20car%20seller%20iSeeCars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20used%20EVs%20with%20the%20largest%20rise%20in%20prices%20were%20Tesla's%20luxury%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-discontinues-model-s-and-x-autonomy-robotaxi-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EModel%20S%20and%20X%20vehicles%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Musk%20announced%20in%20January%20that%20both%20models%20would%20be%20discontinued%20in%20the%20coming%20months%20to%20make%20room%20for%20the%20company's%20Optimus%20robot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spike%20comes%20as%20other%20used%20EVs%20get%20cheaper.%20The%20average%20price%20of%20used%20non-Tesla%20EVs%20fell%203.6%25%20between%20September%20and%20January%2C%20per%20iSeeCars%20data.%20The%20exception%20was%20the%20Porsche%20Taycan%2C%20which%20was%20the%20only%20non-Tesla%20model%20to%20see%20used%20prices%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20auto%20industry%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauto-industry-us-ev-winter-tesla-ford-gm-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEV%20winter%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20prices%20soar%20and%20automakers%20cancel%20new%20models%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20tax%20credit%2C%20electric%20vehicle%20buyers%20are%20turning%20to%20the%20used-car%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESales%20of%20used%20battery-powered%20vehicles%20surged%2021%25%20in%20January%20from%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20per%20data%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coxautoinc.com%2Finsights-hub%2Fev-market-monitor-january-2026%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECox%20Automotive%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20as%20sales%20of%20new%20EVs%20fell%20nearly%2030%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20good%20news%20for%20Tesla.%20The%20brand%20dominates%20the%20used%20EV%20market%20in%20the%20US%2C%20with%20used%20Teslas%20outselling%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAudis%2C%20the%20second-largest%20retailer%2C%20by%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20vehicles%20in%20January%2C%20per%20Cox%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20a%20relief%20for%20Tesla%20owners%2C%20who%20have%20seen%20their%20resale%20values%20collapse%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsed%20Tesla%20prices%20have%20been%20in%20freefall%20since%202022%20and%20hit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-sale-big-losses-second-hand-value-plunge-elon-musk-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enew%20lows%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20backlash%20over%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20gutting%20government%20spending%20through%20his%20role%20at%20DOGE%2C%20which%20he%20has%20since%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20fans%20disappointed%20that%20the%20company%20never%20made%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-promised-25-000-ev-2020-including-inflation-tesla-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elong-promised%20%2425%2C000%20EV%3C%2Fa%3E%20do%20have%20a%20consolation%20prize%20%E2%80%94%20a%20secondhand%20Model%203%20now%20sells%20for%20an%20average%20price%20of%20%2425%2C700.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fused-tesla-prices-soared-end-of-ev-tax-credit-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771587814000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699835c7a645d1188189a75f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fused-tesla-prices-soared-end-of-ev-tax-credit-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20average%20price%20of%20a%20used%20Tesla%20has%20climbed%204.3%25%20since%20the%20end%20of%20the%20%247%2C500%20tax%20credit%20for%20new%20EVs%20in%20September%2C%20according%20iSeeCars.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tcarter%40businessinsider.com%20(Tom%20Carter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fused-tesla-prices-soared-end-of-ev-tax-credit-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranveer%20spotted%20at%20Hospital%20visiting%20Salman's%20father%20Salim%20Khan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771587070000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-128606107%2Cimgsize-25642.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdhurandhar-star-ranveer-singh-spotted-at-lilavati-hospital-visiting-salman-khans-father-salim-khan-watch-video%2Farticleshow%2F128606107.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F128606107.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERanveer%20Singh%20visited%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20on%20Friday%20to%20check%20on%20Salim%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20health.%20The%20veteran%20writer%2C%20admitted%20on%20February%2017%2C%20is%20on%2