.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20custom%20timepieces%20made%20by%20Swiss%20watch%20brand%20Tudor%20for%20employee%20watch%20collector%20clubs%20at%20Apple%20and%20Google%20are%20up%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESilicon%20Valley%20is%20a%20place%20where%20flashy%20watches%20can%20be%20spotted%20on%20the%20wrists%20of%20leaders%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-top-watch-brands-in-silicon-valley-tech-elite-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%20and%20Larry%20Ellison%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20love%20of%20watches%20has%20bred%20collectors'%20groups%20within%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20watch%20made%20for%20an%20employee%20group%20at%20Apple%20is%20up%20for%20bidding%20on%20watch%20auction%20house%20Loupe%20This%2C%20through%20February%2025.%20The%20current%20bid%20as%20of%20Thursday%20afternoon%20stood%20at%20%2413%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20style%20is%20part%20of%20Tudor's%20Black%20Bay%20collection.%20Similar%20pre-owned%20models%20typically%20resell%20for%20around%20%243%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20limited%20Apple%20collectors%20group%20edition%20features%20a%20skull-and-crossbones%20pirate%20flag%20motif%20with%20deep%20ties%20to%20Apple's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tudor%20Black%20Bay%2058%2079030%20Apple%20Employee%20Collectors%20Group%20%26quot%3BPirate%26quot%3B%20Limited%20Edition%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69974f95a645d11881899c47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Tudor%20Black%20Bay%2058%2079030%20%26quot%3BPirate%26quot%3B%20Limited%20Edition%20is%20up%20for%20auction%20on%20Loupe%20This.%3Cp%3ELoupe%20This%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20callback%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-jobs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESteve%20Jobs%20era%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20late%20CEO%20once%20said%20in%20a%20meeting%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20better%20to%20be%20a%20pirate%20than%20join%20the%20Navy%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Macintosh%20team%20often%20referred%20to%20themselves%20as%20pirates%2C%20as%20a%20former%20employee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.folklore.org%2FPirate_Flag.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edescribed%20in%20a%20blog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20a%20nod%20to%20those%20roots%2C%20the%20company%20flew%20a%20pirate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-is-flying-a-pirate-flag-over-its-headquarters-today-heres-why-2016-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eflag%20over%20Apple's%20headquarters%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20its%2040th%20anniversary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2082%20of%20these%20%26quot%3Bpirate%26quot%3B%20watches%20were%20produced%20around%202021%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Loupe%20This%20listing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Tudor%20watch%20created%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Google's%20watch%20collector%20group%2C%20Watches%40%2C%20is%20also%20for%20sale%20on%20the%20vintage%20watch%20marketplace%20Wind%20Vintage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20from%20Tudor's%20Pelagos%20collection%20and%20features%20a%20Google-centric%20twist%20that%20tech%20fans%20may%20recognize%3A%20the%20Google%20Chrome%20Dino%20at%20the%206%20o'clock%20position%20on%20the%20dial.%20The%20design%20is%20inspired%20by%20the%20Chrome%20Dino%20that%20pops%20up%20when%20your%20computer%20isn't%20connected%20to%20the%20internet.%20It's%20also%20the%20character%20in%20a%20game%20you%20can%20play%20on%20Google%20Chrome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20watch%2C%20created%20in%202024%2C%20is%20listed%20for%20%2414%2C900.%20A%20similar%20model%20sold%20at%20an%20auction%20on%20Loupe%20This%20last%20week%20for%20%2410%2C451.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20Pelagos%20models%20are%20reselling%20for%20around%20%244%2C000%20on%20pre-owned%20watch%20marketplaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22TUDOR%20PELAGOS%2025407N%20GOOGLE%20WATCHES%40%20DINO%20TITANIUM%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69974b71f8731049f3af6992%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Google%20Tudor%20Pelagos%2025407N%20sold%20for%20%2410%2C451%20at%20auction.%3Cp%3ELoupe%20This%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EApple%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Tudor%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoupe%20This%20cofounder%20Eric%20Ku%20said%20these%20sorts%20of%20collaborations%20come%20together%20through%20groups%20reaching%20out%20to%20companies%20like%20Tudor%20for%20customized%20watches%20with%20their%20logo%20and%20other%20changes%2C%20like%20an%20engraving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20tend%20to%20sell%20for%20more%20than%20base%20models%20because%20of%20their%20limited%20quantities%2C%20Ku%20said%2C%20and%20they%20attract%20%26quot%3Breal%20fans%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20brands%20they%20represent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20tech%20nerds%20like%20myself%2C%20the%20pirate%20flag%20is%20a%20symbol%20that%20has%20a%20long%20tradition%20of%20being%20used%20by%20the%20Apple%20folks%2C%26quot%3B%20Ku%20said.%20%26quot%3BAlso%2C%20the%20imagery%20of%20that%20pirate%20flag%20is%20quite%20charming.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frare-custom-apple-google-inspired-watches-resale-tudor-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771584481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69975f10a645d11881899e30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frare-custom-apple-google-inspired-watches-resale-tudor-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Watch%20collector%20clubs%20inside%20Apple%20and%20Google%20have%20collaborated%20with%20watchmaker%20Tudor%20on%20limited-edition%20timepieces%20that%20are%20available%20for%20resale.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhart%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frare-custom-apple-google-inspired-watches-resale-tudor-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blue%20Owl%20shopped%20debt%20for%20a%20CoreWeave%20data%20center.%20Lenders%20weren't%20sold.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blue%20Owl%20Data%20Center%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6997898ae1ba468a96ac5a4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBlue%20Owl%20Capital%20failed%20to%20secure%20financing%20for%20a%20%244%20billion%20data%20center%20project%20in%20Pennsylvania.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20lender%20said%20the%20lack%20of%20interest%20was%20due%20to%20CoreWeave's%20creditworthiness.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20data%20center%20investments%20face%20financing%20challenges%20due%20to%20concerns%20about%20credit%20risk.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBlue%20Owl%20Capital%2C%20a%20leading%20investor%20in%20the%20data%20center%20boom%2C%20was%20unable%20to%20arrange%20financing%20for%20a%20%244%20billion%20data%20center%20it%20is%20co-developing%20in%20Pennsylvania%20after%20pitching%20lenders%20to%20help%20bankroll%20the%20project%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20facility%2C%2080%20miles%20west%20of%20Philadelphia%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Lancaster%2C%20will%20be%20occupied%20by%20CoreWeave%2C%20a%20provider%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20cloud%20computing%20services%20that%20has%20become%20a%20closely%20watched%20name%20in%20the%20AI%20race%20for%20its%20rapid%20expansion%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20billions%20of%20dollars%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcore-scientific-shareholder-oppose-coreweave-takeover-bid-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-interest-rate%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20has%20taken%20on%20to%20fuel%20that%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20executive%20who%20arranges%20debt%20for%20major%20data%20center%20deals%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20lack%20of%20interest%20in%20the%20Lancaster%20project%20was%20due%20to%20growing%20caution%20among%20lenders%20and%20investors%20about%20taking%20on%20sizable%20exposures%20to%20AI%20players%20with%20less-than-sterling%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoreWeave%20has%20a%20below-investment-grade%20rating%20of%20B%2B%2C%20according%20to%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20Ratings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20it.%20We%20passed%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20executive%20at%20a%20large%20specialty%20lender%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20financing%20executive%20and%20the%20lender%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20identified%20because%20they%20were%20speaking%20about%20an%20industry%20name%20they%20may%20seek%20to%20do%20business%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesman%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackstone-apollo-blue-owl-data-centers-lease-renewals-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBlue%20Owl%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20the%20company%20had%20%26quot%3Bconsidered%26quot%3B%20third-party%20financing%20for%20the%20Lancaster%20project%20%26quot%3Bas%20we%20would%20with%20any%20transaction%20as%20we%20explore%20alternatives%20before%20choosing%20the%20most%20attractive%20path%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesman%20added%20that%20the%20project%2C%20which%20he%20said%20is%20already%20under%20construction%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20fully%20funded%2C%20on%20time%2C%20and%20on%20budget.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unclear%20whether%20Blue%20Owl%20has%20been%20funding%20construction%20entirely%20from%20its%20own%20capital.%20If%20Blue%20Owl%20is%20unable%20to%20raise%20debt%20for%20the%20Lancaster%20development%2C%20it%20could%20be%20on%20the%20hook%20for%20a%20potentially%20huge%20outlay%20of%20cash%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20data%20center's%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20shows%20the%20complications%20and%20risks%20involved%20in%20financing%20the%20massive%20buildout%20of%20infrastructure%20for%20AI%20computing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrennan%20Hawken%2C%20an%20equity%20analyst%20at%20BMO%20Capital%20Markets%20who%20covers%20Blue%20Owl%2C%20said%20that%20difficulties%20to%20raise%20debt%20for%20the%20Lancaster%20project%20would%20raise%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20familiar%20with%20this%20deal%2C%20but%20if%20there%20is%20a%20struggle%20to%20find%20the%20debt%20financing%2C%20that's%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20red%20flag%20that%20I%20would%20want%20to%20drill%20into%2C%26quot%3B%20Hawken%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20previously%20reported%20that%20major%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foracle-openai-stargate-loans-jpmorgan-diminishing-interest-debt-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebanks%20had%20recent%20difficulty%20selling%3C%2Fa%3E%20off%20pieces%20of%20%2438%20billion%20of%20debt%20to%20finance%20the%20construction%20of%20two%20data%20center%20campuses%20that%20will%20be%20anchored%20by%20Oracle.%20Banks%20often%20sell%20pieces%20of%20such%20large%20commitments%20to%20other%20lenders%20to%20spread%20risk%20and%20also%20reap%20a%20quick%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20slowdown%20in%20interest%20in%20participating%20in%20that%20financing%20was%20due%20to%20worries%20about%20Oracle's%20enormous%20AI%20spending%20and%20whether%20the%20tech%20company's%20credit%20rating%20could%20be%20impacted%20by%20those%20outlays.%20Oracle%20has%20since%20sought%20to%20calm%20the%20lending%20market%2C%20announcing%20that%20it%20would%20raise%20up%20to%20%2450%20billion%20of%20cash%20from%20stock%20and%20bond%20offerings%20in%20order%20to%20%26quot%3Bmaintain%20a%20solid%20investment-grade%20balance%20sheet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e48d3c7d-93c8-469f-803a-1d2ab77f975f%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20the%20boom's%20most%20creative%20financiers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20summer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestors.coreweave.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-details%2F2025%2FCoreWeave-Announces-Multi-Billion-Dollar-Commitment-to-AI-Infrastructure-in-Pennsylvania%2Fdefault.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECoreWeave%20announced%20it%20would%20lease%3C%2Fa%3E%20100%20megawatts%20of%20initial%20capacity%20at%20the%20Lancaster%20data%20center%20and%20potentially%20expand%20its%20commitment%20to%20300%20megawatts.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20would%20pour%20up%20to%20%246%20billion%20into%20the%20project%20to%20equip%20it%20with%20chips%20and%20other%20cloud%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20month%20later%2C%20in%20August%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fchirisatechnologyparks.com%2Fblue-owl-and-chirisa-technology-parks-close-4-billion-joint-venture-partnership-including-machine-investment-group-for-lancaster-campus%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChirisa%20Technology%20Parks%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20would%20partner%20with%20Blue%20Owl%20and%20Machine%20Investment%20Group%20to%20develop%20the%20project.%20The%20partnership%20said%20it%20would%20provide%20%244%20billion%20of%20funding%2C%20an%20amount%20separate%20from%20CoreWeave's%20investment%2C%20to%20support%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20project's%20data%20center%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fall%2C%20Blue%20Owl%20began%20shopping%20the%20development%20to%20potential%20lenders%2C%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20that%20effort%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlue%20Owl%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20creative%20financial%20architects%20of%20the%20data%20center%20building%20boom.%20Last%20year%2C%20it%20structured%20a%20deal%20to%20partner%20with%20Meta%20in%20the%20ownership%20of%20a%20large%20data%20center%20campus%20that%20Meta%20will%20build%20and%20operate%20in%20Louisiana.%20Blue%20Owl%20utilized%20Meta's%20strong%20credit%20to%20raise%20%2427.3%20billion%20of%20investment-grade%20corporate%20bonds%20against%20its%20share%20of%20the%20project's%20equity%2C%20proceeds%20that%20will%20be%20used%20to%20help%20pay%20for%20construction%2C%20according%20to%20S%26amp%3BP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlue%20Owl%20could%20arrange%20a%20similar%20type%20of%20vehicle%20that%20could%20attempt%20to%20tap%20the%20credit%20of%20an%20investment-grade%20customer%20of%20CoreWeave's%20who%20might%20use%20the%20Lancaster%20facility%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-nvidia-coreweave-investment-not-circular-deal-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%2C%20the%20chipmaker%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20has%20purchased%20large%20stakes%20in%20CoreWeave.%20It%20could%20also%20potentially%20raise%20cash%20for%20construction%20debt%20by%20tapping%20large%20institutional%20investor%20clients%20to%20pool%20together%20a%20loan%2C%20Hawken%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20development%20of%20hyperscale%20data%20center%20campuses%20has%20sought%20to%20utilize%20the%20strong%20credit%20ratings%20and%20deep%20pockets%20of%20big-tech%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFluidstack%2C%20a%20peer%20of%20CoreWeave's%2C%20announced%20a%20deal%20last%20year%20to%20lease%20a%20168-megawatt%20data%20center%20in%20Colorado%20City%2C%20Texas%2C%20which%20will%20be%20built%20by%20the%20crypto%20mining%20firm%20Cipher.%20Google%2C%20Fluidstack's%20tenant%20for%20the%20project%2C%20said%20it%20would%20guarantee%20about%20half%20of%20the%20%243%20billion%20due%20under%20the%2010-year%20lease.%20Fluidstack%20signed%20another%20similar-sized%20lease%20in%20December%20with%20the%20data%20center%20builder%20TeraWulf%20that%20will%20also%20provide%20%26quot%3Binvestment-grade%20credit%20support.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-owl-financing-lancaster-data-center-coreweave-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C