20had%20to%20adjust%20to%20the%20streaming%20era.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20while%20AI%20music%20may%20seem%20disruptive%2C%20many%20Wall%20Street%20analysts%20view%20it%20as%20a%20lifeline%20for%20record%20companies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-the-music-industry-is-changing-its-tune-on-ai-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erise%20of%20AI%20music%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20set%20off%20panic%20within%20the%20music%20industry.%20I%20feel%20it%20every%20day%20on%20my%20social%20media%20feeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bands%20I%20follow%20post%20about%20it%20incredulously%2C%20scoffing%20at%20the%20idea%20that%20AI%20could%20replicate%20their%20organic%20magic.%20The%20music%20writers%20I%20follow%20are%20even%20more%20dismissive.%20They%20refuse%20to%20engage%20with%20it%20entirely%2C%20essentially%20closing%20their%20eyes%20and%20willing%20it%20to%20go%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20outside%20of%20my%20middle-aged%20indie-rock%20bubble%2C%20AI%20music%20is%20not%20going%20away.%20It's%20actually%20taking%20over.%20Millennial%20and%20Gen%20Z%20listeners%20are%20embracing%20it%20and%20making%20it%20part%20of%20their%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20survey%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-economy-growth-cycle-copper-prices-korea-stocks-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMorgan%20Stanley%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20more%20than%20half%20of%20listeners%20between%2018%20and%2044%20listened%20to%20an%20average%20of%202%201%2F2%20to%203%20hours%20of%20AI%20music%20a%20week.%20That's%20a%20substantial%20chunk%20of%20time%20%E2%80%94%20about%20the%20length%20of%20a%20Paul%20Thomas%20Anderson%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20markets%20and%20investing%20perspective%2C%20the%20question%20is%20what%20the%20rapid%20rise%20of%20AI%20music%20will%20mean%20for%20publicly%20traded%20record%20labels%20and%20major%20streaming%20platforms.%20The%20labels%20might%20seem%20particularly%20exposed%2C%20since%20they've%20long%20made%20their%20living%20by%20recruiting%20and%20promoting%20human%20artists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20actually%2C%20Wall%20Street%20is%20almost%20unanimously%20bullish%20on%20stocks%20in%20the%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fwmg-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWarner%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fumgnf-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUniversal%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20largely%20because%20their%20artist%20libraries%20are%20still%20immensely%20valuable.%20Lucrative%20licensing%20deals%20are%20already%20being%20inked%2C%20and%20analysts%20expect%20more%20to%20come.%20After%20all%2C%20it's%20tough%20to%20get%20AI%20music%20to%20sound%20just%20like%20Justin%20Bieber%20when%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20catalog%20to%20train%20the%20model%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecord-label%20stocks%20also%20look%20attractive%20right%20now%20because%20they've%20fallen%20so%20much%20throughout%20the%20streaming%20era.%20Both%20Warner%20and%20Universal%20are%20down%20more%20than%2030%25%20from%20highs.%20Any%20upside%20driven%20by%20AI%20music%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20in%20the%20near%20term%20%E2%80%94%20will%20be%20a%20clawback%20of%20value%20erased%20by%20disruption%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F5o08h%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F5o08h%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20how%20can%20we%20forget%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotify-developers-not-writing-code-ai-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%