%20households%20the%20hardest%2C%20reducing%20disposable%20income%20by%20an%20estimated%203.5%20percentage%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FPBop2%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%5B%20Insert%20title%20here%20%5D%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22490%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20who%20is%20paying%20these%20tariffs%2C%20it%20is%20the%20lower-end%20people%20in%20terms%20of%20percentage%20of%20their%20incomes%2C%26quot%3B%20Stiglitz%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20regressive%20and%20it's%20distortive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ba0cde86-b69d-44eb-9d3f-bb40b1f6bd2c%5C%22%3E2.%20Manufacturing%20and%20blue-collar%20jobs%20are%20down%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%20has%20said%20that%20tariffs%20would%20help%20jump-start%20a%20revival%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-masculine-many-manufacturing-jobs-factories-trade-war-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmerica's%20manufacturing%20sector%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20a%20recovery%20isn't%20yet%20visible%20in%20broad-strokes%20employment%20data%2C%20Stiglitz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManufacturing%2C%20one%20of%20the%20US's%20largest%20industries%2C%20is%20estimated%20to%20make%20up%20around%2010%25%20of%20GDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftariffs-wont-bring-manufacturing-jobs-back-wells-fargo-analysts-say-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEmployment%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20sector%20has%20declined%20for%20more%20than%20two%20years%20straight%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20Labor%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%