2cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Infosys-Anthropic%20collaboration%3A%20A%20game-changer%20for%20IT%20sector%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771582111000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-128603054%2Cimgsize-2343121.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Finfosys-anthropic-collaboration-a-game-changer-for-it-sector%2Farticleshow%2F128596452.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Contrary%20to%20initial%20fears%2C%20India's%20IT%20services%20sector%20is%20poised%20to%20benefit%20from%20AI%20advancements%2C%20a%20Jefferies%20report%20suggests.%20Instead%20of%20job%20losses%2C%20companies%20are%20seeing%20increased%20demand%20for%20customized%20AI%20solutions%20built%20on%20proprietary%20data.%20This%20shift%20widens%20the%20industry's%20market%2C%20potentially%20easing%20economic%20concerns%20and%20boosting%20valuations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22War%20rooms%2C%20group%20chats%2C%20and%20video%20games%3A%20Inside%20Elon%20Musk's%20AI%20startup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6997253bf8731049f3af62e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EXAI%20merged%20with%20SpaceX%20and%20lost%20two%20cofounders%20%E2%80%94%20all%20in%20the%20same%20month.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECurrent%20and%20former%20employees%20say%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20increased%20his%20focus%20on%20the%20startup%20over%20the%20past%20six%20months.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWorkers%20detailed%20Musk's%20300-person%20group%20chat%2C%20war%20rooms%2C%20and%20their%20concerns%20about%20safety.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20xAI's%20Palo%20Alto%20headquarters%2C%20engineers%20cheered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20February%202%2C%20and%20they'd%20just%20received%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-acquiring-xai-deal-elon-musk-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ememo%20from%20Elon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20informing%20them%20the%20AI%20startup%20would%20be%20acquired%20by%20his%20rocket%20company%2C%20SpaceX.%20In%20a%20Slack%20channel%20for%20the%20team%20that%20trains%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-grok-training-bias-woke-idealogy-2025-02%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echatbot%20Grok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20memes%20flowed%2C%20and%20a%20few%20changed%20their%20profile%20pictures%20to%20depict%20themselves%20as%20astronauts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20excitement%20was%20quickly%20overshadowed%20by%20the%20pressure%20building%20inside%20the%20startup%20racing%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20rivals%20like%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%2C%20while%20preparing%20for%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-space-stocks-elon-musk-rklb-asts-fly-sats-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexpected%20IPO%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20six%20months%2C%20Musk%20has%20become%20deeply%20involved%20in%20day-to-day%20operations.%20He's%20run%20a%20massive%20group%20chat%20that's%20active%20at%20all%20hours%2C%20directed%20product%20changes%2C%20reassigned%20engineers%2C%20cut%20staff%20on%20key%20teams%2C%20and%20launched%20intensive%20%26quot%3Bwar%20rooms%26quot%3B%20to%20accelerate%20development.%20Several%20current%20and%20former%20employees%20said%20that%20the%20level%20of%20involvement%20has%20altered%20how%20the%20company%20functions.%20Leadership%20roles%20have%20narrowed%2C%20projects%20have%20shifted%20quickly%2C%20and%20teams%20have%20been%20pushed%20into%20what%20one%20described%20as%20a%20constant%20%26quot%3Bfire%20drill.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20that%20the%20changes%20are%20necessary%20as%20the%20company%20scales%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-all-hands-new-structure-recording-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteam's%20lean%20structure%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20the%20secret%20to%20its%20success.%20Discussing%20xAI's%20restructure%20following%20the%20SpaceX%20acquisition%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F2021673886157607383%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20company%20grows%2C%20especially%20as%20quickly%20as%20xAI%2C%20the%20structure%20must%20evolve%20just%20like%20any%20living%20organism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-business%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInside%20Business%3C%2Fa%3E%20stories%20reveal%20the%20inner%20workings%20of%20companies%20from%20Silicon%20Valley%20to%20Wall%20Street%20that%20are%20shaping%20our%20world%20today.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Finside-business%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESign%20up%20for%20the%20newsletter.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22196f1628-a014-4627-91f4-fed1452416bc%5C%22%3EA%20lean%20Musk%20machine%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20memo%20about%20the%20SpaceX%20acquisition%20talked%20of%20building%20a%20%26quot%3Bsentient%20sun%26quot%3B%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-spacex-memo-sentient-sun-kardashev-electromagnetic-mass-driver-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20centers%20in%20space.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Separately%2C%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-sends-staff-q-and-a-on-spacex-merger-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereassured%20staff%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20little%20would%20change%20in%20their%20day-to-day%20work%20as%20the%20company%20geared%20up%20for%20an%20initial%20public%20offering%20that%20could%20value%20it%20at%20%241.5%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20week%2C%20however%2C%20the%20tone%20in%20the%20office%20had%20shifted.%20Two%20of%20the%20company's%20cofounders%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-loses-second-cofounder-jimmy-ba-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJimmy%20Ba%20and%20Tony%20Wu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20announced%20they'd%20resigned%20as%20Musk%20restructured%20the%20company%20and%20narrowed%20their%20responsibilities.%20The%20leadership%20departures%20increase%20risk%20at%20%26quot%3Ba%20sensitive%20stage%26quot%3B%20ahead%20of%20the%20company's%20IPO%2C%20said%20Dimitri%20Zabelin%2C%20a%20senior%20AI%20analyst%20at%20PitchBook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20employee%20described%20co-founder%20Ba's%20departure%20as%20%26quot%3Bincredibly%20disheartening%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20Ba%2C%20who%20studied%20under%20%26quot%3BGodfather%20of%20AI%26quot%3B%20Geoffrey%20Hinton%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20respected%20researchers%20at%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20following%20days%2C%20nearly%20a%20dozen%20employees%20took%20to%20Musk's%20social%20media%20site%20to%20say%20they%20had%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-key-departures-list-elon-musk-startup-cofounders-exodus-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleft%20the%20company%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20had%20departed%20weeks%20earlier.%20A%20few%20left%20of%20their%20own%20volition.%20Others%20were%20affected%20by%20a%20restructuring%20following%20the%20SpaceX%20merger%2C%20in%20which%20Musk%20cut%20some%20members%20of%20the%20teams%20working%20on%20Grok%20Imagine%2C%20the%20chatbot's%20image%20and%20video%20generation%20feature%2C%20and%20the%20Macrohard%20team%2C%20which%20was%20developed%20last%20fall%20to%20help%20automate%20white-collar%20work%2C%20four%20people%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20issue%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20say%20the%20structural%20changes%20%E2%80%94%20coupled%20with%20an%20increasingly%20intense%20work%20culture%20since%20Musk%20wound%20down%20his%20involvement%20in%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-department-of-government-efficiency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDepartment%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20began%20focusing%20more%20on%20the%20AI%20startup%20%E2%80%94%20have%20significantly%20increased%20the%20pace%20and%20pressure%20inside%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20is%20a%20common%20sight%20at%20the%20office.%20Though%20he's%20heavily%20involved%20in%20the%20day-to-day%2C%20Musk%20does%20not%20use%20the%20company's%20Slack%20workspace%2C%20several%20people%20said.%20Instead%2C%20he%20communicates%20frequently%20through%20X%2C%20including%20in%20a%20direct%20message%20group%20of%20more%20than%20300%20engineers.%20Often%2C%20researchers%20will%20drop%20ongoing%20work%20to%20address%20the%20concerns%20that%20Musk%20flags.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20chat%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20it%2C%20Musk%20shares%20screenshots%20of%20his%20conversations%20with%20other%20tech%20executives%20and%20points%20out%20criticisms%20of%20Grok's%20performance%20he%20wants%20addressed.%20Late%20last%20year%2C%20Musk%20told%20staff%20that%20in%20conversations%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20he%20had%20been%20embarrassed%20by%20Grok%20Imagine's%20performance.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20some%20workers%20on%20the%20project%20were%20called%20to%20task%2C%20two%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInternally%2C%20Musk%20has%20expressed%20frustration%20with%20the%20pace%20of%20Grok's%20development.%20XAI%20released%20Grok%204.2%20this%20week.%20Separately%2C%20releases%20of%20at%20least%20two%20other%20products%20were%20pushed%20back%20by%20several%20weeks%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20timelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20instance%20last%20year%2C%20a%20model%20release%20was%20delayed%20for%20several%20days%20because%20Musk%20was%20dissatisfied%20with%20how%20the%20chatbot%20answered%20detailed%20questions%20about%20the%20video%20game%20%26quot%3BBaldur's%20Gate%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%20High-level%20engineers%20were%20pulled%20from%20other%20projects%20to%20improve%20the%20responses%20before%20launch%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20his%20companies%2C%20Musk%20has%20long%20been%20known%20for%20his%20intensity.%20He's%20said%20he%20slept%20on%20Tesla's%20factory%20floor%20during%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-says-model-3-faces-production-hell-2017-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bproduction%20hell%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20Tesla%20Model%203%20in%202017.%20The%20company%20is%20now%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20automaker.%20Now%2C%20xAI%20is%20getting%20the%20same%20treatment.%20Several%20workers%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%2012-%20and%20sometimes%2016-hour%20workdays%20are%20common.%20Two%20said%20managers%20told%20them%20they%20are%20expected%20to%20respond%20to%20Slack%20messages%20within%2030%20minutes%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20time%20of%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20the%20company%20is%20so%20small%2C%20everything%20is%20a%20fire%20drill%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20former%20worker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20any%20given%20time%2C%20multiple%20%26quot%3Bwar%20rooms%26quot%3B%20operate%20out%20of%20conference%20rooms%20at%20the%20company's%20headquarters%20in%20Palo%20Alto%2C%20employees%20said.%20When%20researchers%20are%20%26quot%3Bwar-rooming%2C%26quot%3B%20teams%20temporarily%20relocate%20to%20a%20shared%20space%20to%20work%20side%20by%20side%20on%20specific%20problems%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20for%20months.%20At%20the%20end%20of%202025%2C%20at%20least%20five%20war%20rooms%20were%20running%20simultaneously%2C%20according%20to%20three%20people.%20One%2C%20they%20said%2C%20was%20dedicated%20to%20teaching%20Grok%20how%20to%20play%20one%20of%20Musk's%20favorite%20video%20games%2C%20%26quot%3BLeague%20of%20Legends.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c6fc1cc4-cee8-426d-a1df-33fec277c42b%5C%22%3EShifting%20priorities%20around%20Ani%20and%20safety%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22944%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ani%20AI%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69972564a645d118818994f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221416%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGrok%2FxAI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Musk%20made%20it%20clear%20within%20the%20company%20that%20xAI%20would%20prioritize%20improving%20Ani%2C%20a%20hyper-sexualized%2C%20anime-inspired%20AI%20companion%2C%20people%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20issue%20said.%20He%20characterized%20Ani%2C%20a%20virtual%20companion%20who%20is%20capable%20of%20sexual%20role-play%2C%20as%20a%20way%20to%20set%20xAI%20apart%20from%20other%20AI%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20employees%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they%20were%20unsettled%20by%20the%20company's%20focus%20on%20the%20product.%20Today%2C%20the%20character%20is%20displayed%20prominently%20at%20the%20company's%20headquarters.%20At%20a%20company%20holiday%20party%2C%20paid%20actors%20dressed%20as%20Ani%20and%20another%20character%20hosted%20a%20robot%20fight%20club-style%20event%2C%20according%20to%20videos%20shared%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EROBOT%20CAGE%20MATCHES%20%26amp%3B%20GROK'S%20ANI%20COSPLAY%20AT%20xAI%20HOLIDAY%20PARTY%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20Dec%2021%20bash%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20your%20average%20tech%20mixer...%20xAI%20went%20full%20spectacle%20with%20dancing%20bots%20and%20live%20Optimus%20cage%20matches.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAnd%20a%20cosplayer%20stole%20the%20spotlight%20dressed%20as%20Grok%E2%80%99s%20goth%203D%20persona%20%E2%80%9CAni%2C%E2%80%9D%20doubling%20as%20a%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FllhKdLPjsA%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FllhKdLPjsA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mario%20Nawfal%20(%40MarioNawfal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarioNawfal%2Fstatus%2F2002957266991886385%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2022%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20employees%20said%20they%20had%20joined%20the%20company%20hoping%20to%20work%20on%20systems%20that%20would%20push%20the%20boundaries%20of%20science%20and%20were%20discouraged%20to%20find%20significant%20resources%20devoted%20to%20Ani.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrok's%20behavior%20on%20social%20media%20has%20also%20been%20a%20source%20of%20tension%20inside%20the%20company.%20Musk%20has%20characterized%20xAI%20and%20its%20chatbot%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Banti-woke%26quot%3B%20counterpart%20to%20ChatGPT.%20Public%20backlash%20against%20the%20chatbot%2C%20including%20for%20Grok's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrok-antisemitism-xai-internal-worker-response-slack-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseries%20of%20antisemitic%20rants%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20instances%20in%20which%20it%20digitally%20undressed%20people%20on%20social%20media%20without%20their%20consent%2C%20has%20put%20strain%20on%20employees%2C%20who%20have%20expressed%20concern%20about%20how%20their%20place%20of%20employment%20is%20viewed%20in%20the%20AI%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20last%20year%2C%20the%20company%20did%20not%20have%20a%20team%20of%20researchers%20specifically%20geared%20toward%20working%20on%20safety%20concerns%20associated%20with%20its%20large%20language%20model.%20It%20hired%20its%20first%20dedicated%20safety%20researcher%20in%20February%20of%20last%20year%2C%20around%20the%20same%20time%20that%20the%20Human%20Data%20team%20%E2%80%94%20which%20trains%20the%20chatbot%20%E2%80%94%20began%20reporting%20issues%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-grok-explicit-content-data-annotation-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereviewing%20large%20amounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20X%20user-generated%20requests%20for%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20material.%20One%20person%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20team%20said%20it%20was%20known%20within%20the%20company%20that%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20Grok%20usage%20was%20adult%20role-play%2C%20and%20the%20use%20case%20was%20discussed%20in%20several%20meetings%20with%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20safety%20team%20grew%20to%20roughly%20half%20a%20dozen%20employees%20before%20three%20people%20left%20in%20December%2C%20shortly%20before%20users%20on%20X%20began%20reporting%20instances%20of%20the%20chatbot%20creating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-grok-remove-clothes-ai-images-women-minors-backlash-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enon-consensual%20sexual%20images%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20people%2C%20including%20some%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20team%2C%20xAI's%20safety%20teams%20lacked%20the%20authority%20to%20formally%20block%20product%20launches%20and%20were%20focused%20primarily%20on%20adjusting%20model%20outputs%20after%20training%20rather%20than%20conducting%20broad%20pre-launch%20risk%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F2022696301482381830%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%20that%20%26quot%3Beveryone's%20job%20is%20safety%26quot%3B%20at%20xAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20some%20fake%20department%20with%20no%20power%20to%20assuage%20the%20concerns%20of%20outsiders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXAI%20still%20has%20a%20handful%20of%20workers%20in%20safety%20roles%20and%20was%20hiring%20for%20additional%20safety%20staff%20in%20January%2C%20according%20to%20posts%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20former%20workers%20say%20the%20backlash%20and%20pace%20of%20work%20prompted%20their%20exit.%20Last%20summer%2C%20xAI%20shortened%20its%20vesting%20period%20from%20the%20industry%20standard%20of%20one%20year%20to%20six%20months%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20workers%20to%20leave%20without%20forfeiting%20large%20portions%20of%20their%20equity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployee%20retention%20challenges%20are%20not%20unique%20to%20xAI%3B%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20have%20faced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexecutives-board-members-and-researchers-who-left-openai-in-2025-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewaves%20of%20departures%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20months.%20Across%20the%20industry%2C%20AI%20companies%20are%20competing%20fiercely%20for%20a%20limited%20pool%20of%20top%20researchers%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20have%20begun%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresignation-letters-quit-openai-anthropic-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evoicing%20concern%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20narrowing%20space%20for%20exploratory%20work%20as%20companies%20increasingly%20orient%20themselves%20toward%20product%20over%20research%20in%20the%20competition%20to%20build%20ever%20larger%20models%20%E2%80%94%20a%20dynamic%20that%20poses%20a%20particular%20problem%20for%20xAI%2C%20which%20is%20younger%20and%20smaller%20than%20its%20main%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20some%20analysts%20say%20the%20race%20is%20far%20from%20settled.%20Andrew%20Rocco%2C%20a%20stock%20strategist%20at%20Zacks%20Investment%20Research%2C%20compared%20the%20current%20AI%20landscape%20to%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20Grok%20is%20that%20far%20behind%2C%20and%20it's%20still%20early%20in%20this%20race%2C%26quot%3B%20Rocco%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20publicly%20signaled%20confidence.%20He%20told%20staff%20last%20week%20during%20the%20all-hands%2C%20referencing%20xAI's%20moment%20of%20transition%3A%20%26quot%3BThere's%20some%20people%20who%20are%20better%20suited%20for%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20a%20company%20and%20less%20suited%20for%20the%20later%20stages.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20xAI%20or%20have%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Agkay%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Egkay%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20248-894-6012.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20device%2C%20and%20nonwork%20WiFi%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-leadership-style-big-year-grok-ipo-spacex-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771582081000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69972547e1ba468a96ac4c26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-leadership-style-big-year-grok-ipo-spacex-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20wake%20of%20cofounder%20exits%2C%20Elon%20Musk's%20hands-on%20management%20is%20reshaping%20the%20startup.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gkay%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20Kay)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-leadership-style-big-year-grok-ipo-spacex-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Topless%2C%20brainless%20%26amp%3Bamp%3B%20shameless'%3A%20BJP%20slams%20Cong's%20'despicable'%20act%20at%20AI%20summit%2C%20guns%20for%20Rahul%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771581879000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-128604172%2Cimgsize-64654.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Ftopless-brainless-shameless-centre-slams-congress-after-youth-wings-shirtless-march-at-ai-summit-blames-rahul-gandhi%2Farticleshow%2F128602944.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BJP%20has%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20disrupting%20the%20AI%20Impact%20Summit%20to%20damage%20India's%20global%20image%2C%20alleging%20the%20protest%20was%20directed%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20Youth%20Congress%20workers%20staged%20a%20demonstration%2C%20raising%20slogans%20against%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20leading%20to%20detentions.%20BJP%20leaders%20condemned%20the%20act%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20embarrass%20India%20on%20the%20world%20stage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TikToker%20Khaby%20Lame's%20%24975%20million%20deal%20is%20riding%20on%20a%20crashing%20stock%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222517%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22TikTok%20creator%20Khaby%20Lame.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69961974a645d1188189880b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221678%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETikTok%20creator%20Khaby%20Lame.%3Cp%3EPATRICIA%20DE%20MELO%20MOREIRA%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3BDan%20Whateley%2FBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETikToker%20Khaby%20Lame's%20%24975%20million%20deal%20is%20looking%20increasingly%20shaky.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20stock%20price%20of%20a%20company%20he's%20seeking%20a%20merger%20with%20has%20fallen%20from%20a%20peak%20of%20over%20%24180%20to%20%2411.19.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20is%20pitching%20investors%20on%20using%20an%20AI%20clone%20of%20Lame%20to%20drive%20billions%20in%20e-commerce%20sales.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20superstar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkhaby-lame-business-biggest-tiktok-creator-in-the-world-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKhaby%20Lame%3C%2Fa%3E's%20%24975%20million%20deal%20is%20getting%20squeezed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHong%20Kong-based%20Rich%20Sparkle%20Holdings%20last%20month%20unveiled%20plans%20to%20merge%20with%20Lame's%20social%20media%20and%20e-commerce%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20made%20Lame's%20payout%20dependent%20on%20Rich%20Sparkle's%20share%20price%2C%20which%20has%20plunged%20to%20%2411%20as%20of%20market%20close%20on%20Thursday%20from%20a%20high%20of%20%24180%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELame%2C%20a%20Senegalese-Italian%20creator%2C%20built%20a%20following%20with%20dialogue-free%20videos%20mocking%20overly%20complicated%20life%20hacks%2C%20like%20using%20a%20gadget%20to%20open%20a%20soda%20can%20instead%20of%20just%20popping%20the%20tab.%20He%20is%20now%20the%20world's%20top%20TikTok%20influencer%20with%20over%20160%20million%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20deal%2C%20Rich%20Sparkle%20%E2%80%94%20formerly%20a%20financial%20printing%20company%20%E2%80%94%20planned%20to%20create%20an%20AI%20avatar%20of%20Lame%20to%20do%20brand%20deals%20and%20sell%20products%20on%20social%20media%20while%20earning%20a%20commission.%20Rich%20Sparkle%20projected%20Lame's%20avatar%20could%20drive%20as%20much%20as%20%244%20billion%20in%20annual%20product%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20return%20for%20its%20IP%2C%20Lame's%20company%20would%20get%2075%20million%20new%20shares%20in%20Rich%20Sparkle%2C%20valued%20at%20%2413%20each.%20(That%20%2413%20is%20a%20guide.%20Someone%20actually%20has%20to%20buy%20the%20shares%20for%20Lame%20and%20his%20team%20to%20cash%20out.%20So%2C%20if%20the%20share%20price%20of%20Rich%20Sparkle%20tumbles%2C%20the%20value%20of%20Lame's%20stake%20will%20fall%20as%20well.%20The%20same%20is%20true%20if%20it%20goes%20up.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERich%20Sparkle's%20drop-off%20isn't%20affecting%20Lame's%20current%20wealth%2C%20as%20there%20have%20been%20no%20formal%20filings%20indicating%20that%20the%20deal%20has%20closed%20or%20been%20approved%20by%20the%20Nasdaq.%20Lame%20and%20representatives%20for%20Rich%20Sparkle%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Khaby%20Lame%20attended%20the%20Met%20Gala%20in%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6997a286e1ba468a96ac5b80%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKhaby%20Lame%20attended%20the%20Met%20Gala%20in%202025.%3Cp%3EDia%20Dipasupil%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Nary%2C%20a%20management%20professor%20at%20Wharton%2C%20said%20it's%20hard%20to%20know%20what%20will%20happen%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPublic%20details%20about%20the%20business%20are%20scarce%2C%20and%20the%20company's%20value%20%E2%80%94%20based%20on%20a%20projection%20of%20how%20much%20Lame's%20fame%20could%20be%20worth%20%E2%80%94%20is%20hard%20to%20assess.%20If%20Lame's%20team%20and%20Rich%20Sparkle%20shared%20more%20financial%20information%2C%20it%20could%20boost%20confidence%20in%20the%20company%2C%20Nary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNormally%2C%20you'd%20have%20more%20specifics%20on%20the%20asset%20being%20acquired%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20value%20of%20the%20company%20depends%20on%20that%20person%20and%20his%20related%20ventures.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2296c8a190-bbf7-46ec-bba5-885a165677a8%5C%22%3EWait%2C%20a%20digital%20clone%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20a%20digital%20clone%20of%20Lame%20to%20sell%20stuff%20may%20seem%20like%20a%20wildly%20futuristic%20idea.%20However%2C%20digital%20avatars%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20common%20in%20the%20influencer%20e-commerce%20playbook%2C%20particularly%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChinese%20platforms%20like%20Baidu%2C%20JD.com%2C%20and%20Alibaba's%20Taobao%20have%20become%20hubs%20for%20digital%20avatars%20to%20sell%20on%20livestreams.%20AI%20clones%20of%20celebrities%20or%20influencers%20can%20pull%20in%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20a%20single%20livestream.%20The%20avatar%20for%20one%20Chinese%20influencer%2C%20Luo%20Yonghao%2C%20drove%20over%20%247%20million%20in%20sales%20during%20a%20more%20than%206-hour%20selling%20session%20last%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2025%2F06%2F19%2Fai-humans-in-china-just-proved-they-are-better-influencers.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Khaby%20Lame%20took%20photos%20with%20fans%20during%20a%20September%20visit%20to%20China%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69979343f8731049f3af721c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKhaby%20Lame%20took%20photos%20with%20fans%20during%20a%20September%20visit%20to%20China.%20He%20is%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BSpeechless%20Bro%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20country.%3Cp%3EVCG%2FVCG%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20humans%20can%20appear%20more%20authentic%20to%20viewers%2C%20AI%20avatars%20can%20sell%2024%20hours%20a%20day%20without%20breaks%20and%20answer%20viewers'%20questions%20in%20real%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20an%20hour%2C%20you%20start%20to%20lose%20your%20concentration%2C%20you%20start%20to%20lose%20your%20voice%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alexandre%20Ouairy%2C%20Director%20of%20PLTFRM%2C%20a%20marketing%2C%20advertising%2C%20and%20e-commerce%20agency%20in%20China.%20%26quot%3BA%20machine%20will%20continue%20speaking%20nonstop.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELame%20doesn't%20narrate%20any%20of%20his%20videos%2C%20which%20could%20make%20it%20even%20easier%20for%20his%20digital%20avatar%20to%20succeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20got%20a%20great%20following%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20translate%20to%20a%20parasocial%20relationship%20like%20Mark%20Rober%20or%20Jimmy%20Donaldson%20does%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jim%20Louderback%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreator-platforms-make-more-money-old-media-wpp-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecreator%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E%20advisor%2C%20name-checking%20the%20popular%20science%20influencer%20and%20creator%20behind%20MrBeast.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20the%20character%20he%20built%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-deal-finalized-what-changes-ownership-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eon%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20separate%20from%20himself%2C%20if%20he%20decides%20to%20pull%20back%2C%20his%20character%20lives%20on%20in%20the%20digital%20twinning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERich%20Sparkle's%20plan%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20a%20Chinese%20marketing%20agency%20known%20as%20Three%20Sheep%20Group%2C%20is%20to%20use%20Lame's%20likeness%20to%20craft%20brand%20deals%20and%20sell%20products%20on%20apps%20like%20TikTok%20Shop%2C%20primarily%20in%20the%20US%2C%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20Southeast%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20avatars%20become%20%26quot%3Bthe%20latest%20style%20of%20livestreaming%20in%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20lot%20of%20Chinese%20companies%20believe%20they%20can%20%26quot%3Bcopy%20the%20same%20format%20and%20do%20it%20in%20other%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ophenia%20Liang%2C%20cofounder%20of%20the%20agency%2C%20Digital%20Crew%2C%20which%20helps%20Western%20brands%20break%20into%20the%20Chinese%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20how%20skilled%20Lame's%20partners%20are%20at%20cloning%20his%20likeness%2C%20it%20still%20may%20be%20very%20hard%20to%20translate%20his%20fame%20into%20%244%20billion%20in%20annual%20live-commerce%20sales%2C%20the%20figure%20that%20Rich%20Sparkle%20said%20it%20could%20hit%20in%20its%20acquisition%20announcement%2C%20the%20marketers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhatnot%2C%20a%20buzzy%20platform%20focused%20on%20livestream%20commerce%20in%20the%20US%20and%20a%20few%20other%20markets%2C%20said%20it%20drove%20a%20total%20of%20%248%20billion%20in%202025%20product%20sales%2C%20as%20measured%20by%20gross%20merchandise%20value%20(GMV).%20Rich%20Sparkle's%20estimate%20suggests%20that%20Lame%20himself%20could%20drive%20sales%20equal%20to%20half%20that%20entire%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESales%20on%20other%20top%20US%20social%20commerce%20platforms%20like%20TikTok%20Shop%20are%20growing%20quickly%2C%20but%20are%20still%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20those%20in%20the%20Chinese%20market.%20During%20the%20busiest%20four-day%20stretch%20of%20the%20holiday%20shopping%20season%20last%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-shop-crossed-500-million-in-us-sales-black-friday-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%20Shop%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20its%20total%20US%20sales%20were%20around%20%24500%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsing%20his%20digital%20clone%2C%20there%20would%20be%20good%20revenue%2C%26quot%3B%20Liang%20said%20of%20Lame%2C%20but%20he's%20unlikely%20to%20drive%20%244%20billion%20in%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2236902e2a-5414-41e8-b659-a9ac0c512e34%5C%22%3EInfluencer-fronted%20public%20companies%20have%20struggled%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20influencer%20economy%20is%20a%20buzzy%20category%20among%20investors%2C%20it%20has%20yet%20to%20produce%20an%20enduring%20IPO%20success%20story%2C%20aside%20from%20social%20media%20giants%20like%20Meta%20and%20Reddit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20isn't%20stopping%20some%20creators%20from%20dreaming%20of%20going%20public.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-jimmy-donaldson-burger-venture-implosion-lawsuits-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMrBeast's%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20hinted%20at%20plans%20to%20IPO%2C%20for%20example.%20The%20top%20YouTuber's%20company%20was%20valued%20at%20around%20%245%20billion%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-bitmine-immersion-investment-youtube-jimmy-donaldson-crypto-tom-lee-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elatest%20funding%20round%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20creator%20MrBeast%20(Jimmy%20Donaldson).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6944374564858d02d21710f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYouTube%20creator%20MrBeast%20(Jimmy%20Donaldson).%3Cp%3EMichael%20M.%20Santiago%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELame%20is%20looking%20to%20enter%20the%20public%20markets%20through%20a%20reverse%20merger.%20That's%20when%20a%20private%20company%20goes%20public%20by%20merging%20with%20an%20existing%20public%20company%2C%20often%20called%20a%20shell.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20the%20shell%20is%20Rich%20Sparkle%2C%20incorporated%20in%20the%20British%20Virgin%20Islands%2C%20with%20its%20main%20financial%20printing%20business%20based%20in%20Hong%20Kong.%20It%20reported%20%246.2%20million%20in%20revenue%20in%20its%202025%20fiscal%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20reverse%20merger%20can%20be%20a%20way%20to%20access%20public%20markets%20with%20less%20time%2C%20cost%2C%20and%20scrutiny%20than%20a%20traditional%20IPO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20think%20of%20reverse%20mergers%20as%20a%20poor%20man's%20IPO%2C%20because%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20spend%20all%20this%20money%20to%20get%20listed%2C%20and%20it's%20much%20cheaper%20than%20going%20through%20the%20IPO%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tim%20Loughran%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Notre%20Dame's%20Mendoza%20College%20of%20Business.%20%26quot%3BFor%20investors%2C%20they%20should%20be%20wary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20creator%20economy%20firms%20have%20opted%20for%20reverse%20mergers%20to%20list%20on%20public%20markets%2C%20including%20the%20video%20app%20Triller%20and%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20influencer%20collective%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencers-describe-problems-at-clubhouse-media-group-content-mansions-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClubhouse%20Media%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Clubhouse%20shrunk%20down%20to%20a%20penny%20stock%20and%20is%20now%20traded%20over%20the%20counter.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-challenger-triller-delisted-from-the-nasdaq-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETriller%20was%20delisted%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Nasdaq%20in%20December%20after%20failing%20to%20file%20its%20SEC%20paperwork%20on%20time.%20Its%20market%20cap%20has%20fallen%20over%2090%25%20from%20its%20first%20day%20of%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20risk%20of%20running%20an%20influencer-fronted%20public%20company%20is%20reliance%20on%20a%20single%20personality%20to%20drive%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGaming%20and%20esports%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffaze-clan-decline-says-more-about-influencer-startups-than-esports-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFaZe%20Clan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20went%20public%20in%202022%20via%20a%20special-purpose%20acquisition%20company%20valued%20at%20%24725%20million%2C%20relied%20on%20one%20creator%20for%20about%2020%25%20of%20its%20revenue.%20It%20sold%20itself%20in%202023%20for%20a%20fraction%20of%20its%20SPAC%20price%2C%20and%20its%20influencer%20business%20later%20unraveled%20in%20late%202025%20after%20many%20of%20its%20top%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffaze-clans-creator-exodus-spotlights-a-key-business-risk-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etalent%20left%20abruptly%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20a%20contract%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20very%20difficult%20to%20have%20an%20IPO%20for%20a%20company%20that's%20based%20entirely%20on%20an%20influencer%20and%20personality%2C%26quot%3B%20Wharton's%20Nary%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20precisely%20a%20case%20of%20an%20asset%20that%20would%20be%20very%20hard%20to%20value%20and%20take%20through%20a%20standard%20IPO%20process.%20Having%20a%20key%20man%20risk%2C%20it's%20tough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20the%20reporters%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Almoses%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Elmoses%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Adwhateley%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Edwhateley%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20or%20on%20Signal%20at%20%40danwhateley.94.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktoker-khaby-lame-975-million-deal-riding-on-falling-stock-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771581721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69961988a645d11881898810%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktoker-khaby-lame-975-million-deal-riding-on-falling-stock-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Nasdaq-li