ta-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Dario%20Amodei%20went%20viral%20for%20refusing%20to%20join%20together%20in%20a%20sign%20of%20unity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOnce%20colleagues%2C%20the%20two%20AI%20CEOs%20have%20helped%20nurse%20their%20companies'%20rivalry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20how%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20finally%20reached%20this%20point.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20know%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20rivalries%20in%20AI%2C%20just%20ask%20for%20a%20show%20of%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20and%20Anthropic%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdario-amodei%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDario%20Amodei%3C%2Fa%3E%20provided%20what%20is%20sure%20to%20become%20an%20iconic%20image%20of%20their%20feud.%20The%20pair%20went%20viral%20for%20refusing%20to%20join%20hands%20as%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world's%20tech%20leaders%20gathered%20for%20a%20moment%20of%20unity%2C%20sparked%20by%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20a%20timeline%20of%20how%20Altman%20and%20Amodei%20went%20from%20colleagues%20to%20becoming%20the%20face%20of%20AI's%20Cold%20War.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJuly%202015%3A%20Decisions%20happened%20over%20dinner%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%2C%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20and%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20financial%20columnist%20Andrew%20Ross%20Sorkin%20sitting%20in%20chairs%20onstage%20during%20the%20Vanity%20Fair%20New%20Establishment%20Summit%20in%202015%20in%20San%20Francisco.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64482a9290523900196fe2e0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221995%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20and%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20financial%20columnist%20Andrew%20Ross%20Sorkin%20speak%20onstage%20during%20%26quot%3BWhat%20Will%20They%20Think%20of%20Next%3F%20Talking%20About%20Innovation%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20Vanity%20Fair%20New%20Establishment%20Summit%20at%20Yerba%20Buena%20Center%20for%20the%20Arts%20on%20October%206%2C%202015%2C%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20California.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Kovac%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202015%2C%20Tesla%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Altman%2C%20and%20a%20group%20of%20elite%20AI%20researchers%20all%20gathered%20at%20the%20swanky%20Rosewood%20Hotel%20in%20Menlo%20Park%2C%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20The%20New%20York%20Times%2C%20Musk%20had%20a%20falling%20out%20with%20then-Google%20CEO%20Larry%20Page.%20Weeks%20later%2C%20Musk%2C%20Altman%2C%20Amodei%2C%20Greg%20Brockman%2C%20Ilya%20Sutskever%2C%20and%20others%20discussed%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20new%20AI%20lab%20to%20ensure%20Google%20had%20a%20worthy%20competitor%20in%20the%20AI%20space.%20Musk%20invited%20Amodei%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkantrowitz.medium.com%2Fthe-making-of-anthropic-ceo-dario-amodei-449777529dd6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%3C%2Fa%3E%20tech%20journalist%20Alex%20Kantrowitz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20vision%20became%20OpenAI%2C%20though%20Amodei%20initially%20elected%20not%20to%20join%20the%20startup%20research%20lab.%20Roughly%20a%20year%20later%2C%20he%20changed%20his%20mind%20and%20joined%20OpenAI%20as%20%26quot%3BTeam%20Lead%20for%20AI%20Safety.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESeptember%202018%3A%20Amodei%20rises%20up%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dario%20Amodei%20speaks%20at%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6977ededa645d118818804e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%3Cp%3EMarkus%20Schreiber%2FFile%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmodei%20quickly%20moved%20up%20the%20ranks%20at%20OpenAI.%20In%20September%202018%2C%20the%20startup%20named%20him%20its%20research%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%2C%20who%20cofounded%20OpenAI%20while%20still%20serving%20as%20president%20of%20Y%20Combinator%2C%20began%20to%20devote%20more%20time%20to%20the%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202019%2C%20Altman%20stepped%20down%20as%20YC's%20leader.%20He%20then%20became%20CEO%20of%20OpenAI%20and%20led%20the%20startup's%20pivot%20to%20a%20capped%20for-profit%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202019%2C%20OpenAI%20released%20GPT-2%2C%20which%20Amodei%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20developing.%20A%20month%20later%2C%20OpenAI%20named%20Amodei%20as%20its%20Vice%20President%20of%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJune%202020%3A%20OpenAI%20releases%20GPT-3%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202020%2C%20OpenAI%20began%20to%20show%20just%20how%20far%20the%20technology%20had%20come%20with%20the%20release%20of%20GPT-3%2C%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20first%20highly%20capable%20Large%20Language%20Model%20(LLM).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmodei%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20that%20the%20model%20had%20%26quot%3Bthis%20emergent%20quality.%26quot%3B%20Independent%20researchers%20told%20the%20publication%20that%20GPT-3's%20capabilities%20surprised%20them%2C%20even%20as%20the%20model%20still%20showed%20signs%20of%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20safety%20concerns%2C%20OpenAI%20initially%20controlled%20access%20through%20a%20private%20beta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDecember%202020%3A%20Amodei%20goes%20his%20own%20way%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%20at%20The%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20Davos%2C%20Switzerland.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6983b5fbd3c7faef0ecda1f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnthropic%20CEO%20Dario%20Amodei%20at%20The%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20Davos%2C%20Switzerland.%3Cp%3EFortune%20via%20Reuters%20Connect%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20GPT-3%20solidified%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Findustries-openai-is-disrupting-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E's%20standing%2C%20but%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20tensions%20were%20rising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rifts%20began%20when%20Amodei%20successfully%20lobbied%20to%20keep%20Greg%20Brockman%2C%20an%20OpenAI%20cofounder%2C%20off%20the%20team%20that%20developed%20GPT-3%2C%20according%20to%20Keach%20Hagey's%20biography%20of%20Altman%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Optimist%3A%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20the%20Race%20to%20Invent%20the%20Future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHagey%20wrote%20that%20Amodei's%20stunning%20power%20within%20OpenAI%20had%20started%20to%20ruffle%20feathers.%20Differences%20continued%20to%20escalate%20over%20Amodei's%20long-held%20views%20on%20safety%2C%20Hagey%20wrote%2C%20especially%20regarding%20slowing%20the%20pace%20of%20updates%20to%20prevent%20malicious%20uses%20of%20the%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmodei%20told%20friends%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bfelt%20psychologically%20abused%20by%20Altman%2C%26quot%3B%20Hagey%20wrote.%20Altman%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20was%20telling%20colleagues%20that%20the%20tension%20%26quot%3Bwas%20making%20him%20hate%20his%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2029%2C%202020%2C%20OpenAI%20made%20it%20official.%20Amodei%20was%20leaving%2C%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bhandful%26quot%3B%20of%20other%20colleagues%20were%20leaving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmodei%20has%20since%20suggested%20that%20his%20vision%20became%20incompatible%20with%20OpenAI's%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20incredibly%20unproductive%20to%20try%20and%20argue%20with%20someone%20else's%20vision%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20told%20podcaster%20Lex%20Friedman%20in%202024%2C%20when%20asked%20why%20he%20left%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEarly%202021%3A%20Anthropic%20is%20created%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22anthropic%20talk%20to%20claude%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698f4e40a645d11881894e50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222081%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJakub%20Porzycki%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20seven%20other%20former%20OpenAI%20employees%2C%20Amodei%20founded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdario-amodei-anthropic-profit-pressure-versus-safety-mission-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20early%202021.%20The%20group%20was%20extremely%20close%20and%20included%20Daniela%20Amodei%2C%20Dario's%20sister.%20Daniela%20Amodei%20later%20said%20the%20name%20was%20chosen%20to%20emphasize%20their%20company's%20focus%20on%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20one%20of%20Anthropic's%20initial%20employees%20hadn't%20worked%20at%20OpenAI%2C%20according%20to%20AI%20Business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20starting%20from%20scratch%2C%20Amodei%20said%20that%20by%20the%20Summer%20of%202022%2C%20the%20company's%20chatbot%2C%20Claude%2C%20had%20finished%20training.%20Amodei%20said%20he%20was%20worried%20about%20what%20the%20release%20of%20a%20powerful%20AI%20could%20mean.%20Anthropic%20held%20off%20on%20a%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20suspect%20it%20was%20the%20right%20thing%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20told%20Time%20Magazine%20in%202024.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it's%20not%20totally%20clear-cut.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonths%20later%2C%20OpenAI%20released%20ChatGPT%2C%20kicking%20off%20the%20AI%20race%20and%20making%20Amodei's%20former%20employer%20a%20household%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMay%202024%3A%20Amodei%20takes%20a%20shot%20%E2%80%A6%20or%20did%20he%3F%3Cp%3EAs%20Anthropic%20began%20to%20establish%20itself%20in%20its%20own%20right%2C%20Amodei%20began%20to%20use%20his%20public%20appearances%20to%20take%20what%20were%20widely%20viewed%20as%20implicit%20shots%20at%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20appearance%20at%20a%20Bloomberg%20event%2C%20Amodei%20noted%20how%20Anthropic%20had%20kept%20its%20leadership%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%207%20cofounders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20Gizmodo%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgizmodo.com%2Fanthropic-founders-publicly-needle-openai-execs-1851467231%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThree%20and%20a%20half%20years%20later%2C%20we're%20all%20still%20at%20the%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20never%20calling%20out%20by%20name%2C%20OpenAI%20was%20experiencing%20upheaval%20at%20the%20time.%20Months%20earlier%2C%20Andrej%20Karpathy%2C%20an%20OpenAI%20cofounder%2C%20had%20left%20the%20company.%20And%20in%20November%202023%2C%20Altman%20was%20briefly%20pushed%20out%20of%20OpenAI%2C%20an%20effort%20fellow%20cofounder%20Ilya%20Sutskever%20assisted.%20(Sutskever%20later%20expressed%20regret%20over%20his%20role.%20He%20formally%20left%20OpenAI%20just%20days%20after%20Amodei's%20jab%2C%20though%20there%20had%20been%20months%20of%20speculation%20surrounding%20Sutskever's%20standing.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDecember%202025%3A%20'We%20don't%20have%20to%20do%20any%20code%20reds'%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman%20looks%20down%20during%20an%20OpenAI%20event%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69725e7ad3c7faef0eccbed7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221678%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202025%2C%20OpenAI's%20lead%20in%20the%20AI%20race%20was%20slipping.%20When%20presented%20with%20the%20opportunity%2C%20Amodei%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ceo-dario-amodei-drags-openai-and-google-code-red-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eseized%20the%20moment%20to%20troll%20his%20rival.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJournalist%20Andrew%20Ross%20Sorkin%20asked%20Amodei%20about%20OpenAI's%20decision%20to%20declare%20a%20%26quot%3Bcode%20red%26quot%3B%20to%20marshal%20resources%20for%20ChatGPT%20amid%20Google's%20rising%20strength.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20privileged%20position%20where%20we%20can%20just%20keep%20growing%20and%20just%20keep%20developing%20our%20models%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20have%20to%20do%20any%20code%20reds%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20told%20Sorkin%20during%20an%20appearance%20at%20The%20New%20York%20Times'%20DealBook%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20their%20conversation%2C%20Amodei%20appeared%20to%20take%20another%20swipe%20at%20Altman%20when%20he%20talked%20about%20some%20players%20%26quot%3Bwho%20are%20YOLOing%26quot%3B%20by%20making%20too%20risky%20bets%20on%20future%20demand%20based%20on%20their%20current%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20is%20YOLOing%3F%26quot%3B%20Sorkin%20asked.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20going%20to%20answer%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Amodei%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFebruary%202025%3A%20A%20snarky%20Super%20Bowl%20ad%20gets%20a%20response%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20still%20from%20Anthropic's%20ad%20that%20is%20set%20to%20air%20during%20the%20Super%20Bowl%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69835c6ea645d1188188a737%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20still%20from%20Anthropic's%20ad%20is%20set%20to%20air%20during%20the%20Super%20Bowl.%20The%20ad%20features%20a%20scrawny%20man%20who%20wants%20to%20get%20a%20six-pack%20quickly%2C%20but%20a%20helpful%20trainer%20gives%20him%20more%20than%20just%20the%20advice%20he%20needs.%3Cp%3EAnthropic%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20used%20the%20biggest%20stage%20available%20to%20take%20its%20most%20direct%20shot%20yet%20at%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-super-bowl-openai-chatgpt-ads-claude-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Super%20Bowl%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Anthropic%20revealed%20it%20was%20spending%20millions%20on%20an%20advertising%20campaign%20to%20denounce%20AI%20chatbot%20ads.%20While%20OpenAI%20was%20not%20named%20directly%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20who%20the%20intended%20target%20was%2C%20given%20that%20just%20months%20earlier%2C%20OpenAI%20had%20said%20it%20would%20begin%20testing%20ads%20on%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ads%20featured%20real%20human%20actors%20mimicking%20the%20voice%20of%20product-pushing%20AI%20chatbots%20when%20asked%20questions%20like%20how%20to%20get%20a%20six-pack%20quickly%20or%20how%20to%20better%20connect%20with%20your%20mom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20the%20good%20part%20of%20the%20Anthropic%20ads%3A%20they%20are%20funny%2C%20and%20I%20laughed%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fsama%2Fstatus%2F2019139174339928189%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20lengthy%20post%20on%20X.%26quot%3B%20But%20I%20wonder%20why%20Anthropic%20would%20go%20for%20something%20so%20clearly%20dishonest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAltman%20wasn't%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnthropic%20serves%20an%20expensive%20product%20to%20rich%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20glad%20they%20do%20that%20and%20we%20are%20doing%20that%20too%2C%20but%20we%20also%20feel%20strongly%20that%20we%20need%20to%20bring%20AI%20to%20billions%20of%20people%20who%20can't%20pay%20for%20subscriptions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDays%20later%2C%20the%20companies%20went%20head-to-head%20again.%20This%20time%2C%20with%20the%20release%20of%20major%20updates%20to%20their%20coding-focused%20model%20within%20minutes%20of%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFebruary%202025%3A%20I%20(don't)%20want%20to%20hold%20your%20hand%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225365%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20holds%20hands%20with%20Sundar%20Pichai%20and%20Sam%20Altman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6997907da645d1188189a44a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223576%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20a%20moment%20before%20the%20viral%20photo%2C%20Altman%20holds%20hands%20with%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20with%20his%20back%20facing%20toward%20Amodei%3Cp%3ELudovic%20Marin%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20who's%20who%20of%20AI%20and%20tech%20elite%20gathered%20in%20India%20for%20a%20major%20summit%20on%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndian%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20took%20the%20opportunity%20to%20orchestrate%20a%20classic%20image%20of%20unity%3A%20competing%20CEOs%20with%20their%20hands%20raised%20together.%20(It's%20something%20Modi%20has%20done%20before%20with%20other%20world%20leaders%2C%20and%20politicians%20have%20been%20doing%20forever.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EModi%20almost%20got%20his%20moment.%20While%20Altman%20held%20the%20prime%20minister's%20hand%2C%20the%20OpenAI%20CEO%20didn't%20grasp%20Amodei's%20hand%2C%20who%20was%20positioned%20to%20his%20other%20side.%20Amodei%20grasped%20the%20hand%20of%20the%20other%20person%20next%20to%20him%2C%20but%20not%20Altman's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20internet%2C%20predictably%2C%20had%20a%20field%20day.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-leaders-india-summit-awkward-photo-hands-modi-altman-amodei-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnd%20the%20world%20got%20a%20perfect%20encapsulation%20of%20one%20of%20AI's%20bitter%20rivalries.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-dario-amodei-anthropic-openai-ri