sion%20of%20him%20that's%20spreading%20online.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EScholars%20say%20a%20possible%20legal%20challenge%20hinges%20on%20money%20and%20First%20Amendment%20concerns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20conflict%20highlights%20a%20growing%20battle%20over%20AI%20afterlives.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20Adams%20once%20sounded%20open%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-granted-patent-for-ai-llm-bot-dead-paused-accounts-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edigital%20afterlife%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%20that%20he's%20passed%2C%20social%20media%20posts%20attributed%20to%20his%20family%20say%20an%20AI%20version%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BDilbert%26quot%3B%20creator%20circulating%20online%20is%20unauthorized%20%E2%80%94%20and%20deeply%20distressing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202021%20podcast%20clip%2C%20the%20cartoonist%20said%20he%20granted%20%26quot%3Bexplicit%20permission%26quot%3B%20for%20anyone%20to%20make%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftimbaland-posthumous-ai-generated-notorious-big-album-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eposthumous%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20on%20him%2C%20arguing%20that%20his%20public%20thoughts%20and%20words%20are%20%26quot%3Bso%20pervasive%20on%20the%20internet%26quot%3B%20that%20he'd%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20good%20candidate%20to%20turn%20into%20AI.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20he%20was%20OK%20with%20an%20AI%20version%20of%20him%20saying%20new%20things%20after%20he%20died%2C%20as%20long%20as%20they%20seemed%20compatible%20with%20what%20he%20might%20say%20while%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%2068-year-old's%20January%20death%20from%20complications%20of%20metastatic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrity-deaths-famous-people-who-died-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprostate%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20AI-generated%20%26quot%3BScott%20Adams%26quot%3B%20account%20began%20posting%20videos%20of%20a%20digital%20version%20of%20the%20cartoonist%20speaking%20directly%20to%20viewers%20about%20current%20events%20and%20philosophy%2C%20mirroring%20the%20cadence%20and%20topics%20the%20actual%20human%20Adams%20discussed%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20family%20says%20it's%20a%20violation%2C%20not%20a%20tribute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20February%205%20post%20on%20Adams'%20official%20account%20attributed%20to%20his%20brother%2C%20Dave%20Adams%2C%20insisted%20the%20cartoonist%20%26quot%3Bnever%20intended%2C%20never%20would%20have%20approved%20an%20AI%20version%20of%20him%20that%20wasn't%20authorized%20by%20himself%20or%20his%20estate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20real%20Scott%20Adams%20gave%20explicit%20permission%20on%20the%20record%20multiple%20times%20for%20people%20to%20create%20and%20operate%20an%20AI%20version%20of%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20AI%20Adams%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20February%205.%20%26quot%3BSo%20this%20iteration%20exists%20as%20a%20direct%20fulfillment%20of%20that%20stated%20wish.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20Adams%20account%20reiterated%20the%20family's%20objection%20on%20February%2017%2C%20saying%20the%20estate%20was%20%26quot%3Bkindly%20but%20firmly%26quot%3B%20asking%20anyone%20using%20AI%20to%20recreate%20his%20voice%20or%20likeness%20to%20stop%2C%20calling%20the%20digital%20replicas%20a%20%26quot%3Bfabricated%20version%26quot%3B%20of%20Adams%20that%20is%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20distressing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20tribute.%20It%20is%20not%20an%20honor.%20It%20is%20an%20unauthorized%20use%20of%20identity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20post%20read.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20Adams%20estate%20and%20the%20AI%20Adams%20account%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dispute%20underscores%20the%20growing%20legal%20and%20ethical%20fault%20lines%20around%20%26quot%3BAI%20afterlives%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20quickly%20technology%20can%20outpace%20the%20rules%20meant%20to%20govern%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ede86df9-a549-418f-9be2-7ea2a823f029%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'It's%20a%20deepfake'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKaren%20North%2C%20a%20University%20of%20Southern%20California%20professor%20specializing%20in%20digital%20social%20media%20and%20psychology%2C%20said%20calling%20the%20AI-generated%20Adams%20an%20avatar%2C%20as%20some%20have%20online%2C%20softens%20what%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fwhat-is-deepfake%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20deepfake%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20North%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20troubling%20part%2C%20she%20said%2C%20is%20how%20a%20realistic%20imitation%20can%20surface%20while%20a%20family%20is%20grieving%20and%20potentially%20say%20things%20the%20real%20person%20never%20would%20have%20said.%20North%20added%20that%20since%20many%20Americans%20are%20%26quot%3Bgiving%20up%20so%20much%20information%26quot%3B%20through%20apps%20that%20capture%20faces%20and%20voices%20and%20viral%20quizzes%20that%20collect%20personal%20details%2C%20it%20is%20increasingly%20easy%20to%20recreate%20someone%20without%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20find%20it%20very%20disturbing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetsy%20Rosenblatt%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-sora-intellectual-property-video-response-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eintellectual%20property%3C%2Fa%3E%20lawyer%20and%20professor%20at%20Case%20Western%20Reserve%20University%2C%20said%20her%20initial%20reaction%20was%20that%20the%20AI%20Adams%20is%20%26quot%3Bunethical%20in%20the%20extreme.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20die%2C%20they%20die%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegally%2C%20she%20said%2C%20the%20central%20issue%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencer-usage-rights-in-brand-contracts-explained-by-lawyer-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eright%20of%20publicity%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20protections%20over%20a%20person's%20name%2C%20image%2C%20and%20likeness.%20Still%2C%20those%20laws%20are%20more%20focused%20on%20privacy%20and%20economics%20than%20on%20grief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20right%20of%20publicity%20is%20%26quot%3Bchiefly%20concerned%20with%20economic%20remedies%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenblatt%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strongest%20claims%20typically%20involve%20money%3A%20an%20AI%20version%20could%20harm%20existing%20deals%20tied%20to%20Adams'%20identity%20or%20block%20the%20family%20from%20striking%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosenblatt%20described%20two%20potential%20economic%20harms%3A%20%26quot%3BOne%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20that%20it%20could%20be%20harming%20some%20financial%20arrangement%20that%20they%20already%20have.%20Another%20is%20that%20it%20might%20stand%20in%20the%20way%20of%20their%20making%20some%20competitive%20financial%20arrangement%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20account%20appears%20to%20be%20anonymous%3B%20however%2C%20that%20wouldn't%20necessarily%20prevent%20a%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20sue%20somebody%20who%20is%20anonymous%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenblatt%20said%2C%20and%20courts%20can%20allow%20subpoenas%20to%20uncover%20identifying%20information%2C%20though%20it's%20%26quot%3Bnot%20necessarily%20easy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20legal%20analysis%20also%20hinges%20on%20whether%20the%20account%20is%20commercial.%20Courts%20often%20ask%20whether%20the%20speech%20proposes%20a%20commercial%20transaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20digital%20replica%20isn't%20selling%20anything%2C%20Rosenblatt%20said%2C%20it%20becomes%20%26quot%3Bmore%20likely%20to%20be%20considered%20a%20First%20Amendment%20protected%20expression%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20anonymous%20creator%20%E2%80%94%20not%20a%20%26quot%3Bslam%20dunk%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20a%20stronger%20argument.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20Adams%20identifies%20itself%20as%20artificial%20intelligence%20at%20the%20start%20of%20its%20clips%20and%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20solicit%20money.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20February%201%20post%2C%20it%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20original%20Scott's%20gone%2C%20passed%20on%2C%20but%20the%20thinking%20survives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2289ddc000-9696-4f8a-bfec-1dee9695904b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsent%20isn't%20the%20same%20as%20a%20contract%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20estate's%20objections%20sit%20uneasily%20alongside%20Adams'%202021%20comments%20offering%20%26quot%3Bexplicit%20permission%26quot%3B%20for%20AI%20versions%20of%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorth%20said%20offhand%20remarks%20about%20technology%20shouldn't%20automatically%20be%20treated%20as%20binding%20authorization.%20Adams%20was%20%26quot%3Ban%20incredibly%20bright%2C%20incredibly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewspapers-are-dropping-dilbert-after-the-creators-racist-rants-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecreative%20person%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20who%20often%20pushed%20boundaries%2C%20she%20said%2C%20and%20comments%20made%20in%20conversation%20%26quot%3Bmay%20not%20be%20legally%20binding%20in%20ways%20contracts%20and%20intellectual%20property%20rights%20are%20legally%20binding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet%20this%20be%20a%20warning%20to%20all%20of%20us%3A%20be%20careful%20what%20you%20say%2C%20because%20he's%20now%20put%20his%20loved%20ones%20in%20a%20difficult%20position%20as%20they%20protect%20his%20legacy%2C%26quot%3B%20North%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERosenblatt%20said%20Adams'%20wishes%20%26quot%3Bwould%20certainly%20matter%20in%20an%20ethical%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20may%20not%20matter%20legally%20%26quot%3Bunless%20he%20gave%20somebody%20the%20legal%20rights%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20comprehensive%20federal%20law%20governing%20posthumous%20AI%20likeness%2C%20but%20some%20states%20%E2%80%94%20like%20New%20York%20and%20California%20%E2%80%94%20have%20recently%20enacted%20laws%20requiring%20consent%20from%20heirs%20or%20estate%20executors%20before%20creating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgaming-strikes-actors-developers-ai-protections-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edigital%20replicas%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20legal%20questions%20lies%20a%20deeper%20ethical%20one%3A%20who%20controls%20a%20person's%20persona%20after%20they're%20gone%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorth%20said%20people%20%26quot%3Bshould%20own%20the%20rights%20to%20our%20own%20personas%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20when%20they%20die%2C%20those%20rights%20%26quot%3Bshould%20go%20to%20our%20loved%20ones%2C%26quot%3B%20not%20become%20a%20free-for-all.%20AI%20replicas%2C%20she%20warned%2C%20can%20drift%20off-brand%20or%20reshape%20public%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShakespeare%20should%20always%20sound%20like%20Shakespeare%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BDr.%20Seuss%20should%20always%20sound%20like%20Dr.%20Seuss.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20AI%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdilbert-creator-scott-adams-final-message-about-finding-success-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EScott%20Adams%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20fight%20is%20one%20family's%20public%20line-drawing%20exercise.%20It%20may%20also%20be%20a%20preview%20of%20a%20broader%20reckoning%20in%20a%20world%20where%20convincing%20digital%20imitations%20are%20easy%20to%20make%20%E2%80%94%20and%20where%20the%20law%20is%20still%20struggling%20to%20answer%20who%20gets%20to%20decide%20whether%20the%20dead%20keep%20talking%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscott-adams-death-ai-avatar-resurrection-ethics-debate-family-backlash-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771578841000%2C%22visual