oilet%20maker%20Toto%2C%20famous%20for%20its%20high-tech%20bidets%20and%20heated%20seats%2C%20has%20drawn%20investor%20attention.%20The%20company%20makes%20electrostatic%20chucks%2C%20which%20are%20critical%20components%20used%20in%20the%20production%20of%20NAND%20memory%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmemory-chip-shortage-apple-earnings-first-quarter-tim-cook-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMemory%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20climbed%20sharply%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20driven%20by%20AI-related%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20UK-based%20activist%20fund%20Palliser%20Capital%20called%20Toto%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20undervalued%20and%20overlooked%20AI%20memory%20beneficiary%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20reports%20by%20Bloomberg%20and%20the%20Financial%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20news%20broke%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20Palliser%20Capital%20had%20taken%20a%20stake%20and%20was%20pushing%20Toto%20to%20promote%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frare-earths-tech-war-explainer-chips-ai-china-us-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echip-parts%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20toilet%20maker's%20stock%20jumped%20more%20than%205%25.%20Its%20shares%20are%20up%20more%20than%2054%25%20over%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20Toto.%20Japanese%20food%20giant%20Ajinomoto%2C%20better%20known%20for%20its%20umami%20seasonings%20and%20soup%20bases%2C%20has%20become%20an%20unlikely%20AI%20infrastructure%20play.%20The%20company%20produces%20an%20insulating%20material%20used%20in%20advanced%20semiconductor%20packaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAjinomoto's%20latest%20financials%20point%20to%20strength%20beyond%20its%20core%20food%20business.%20For%20the%20nine%20months%20ended%20December%2C%20the%20company%20reported%20an%208.9%25%20rise%20in%20net%20profit%2C%20while%20operating%20profit%20increased%205.6%25%20year-on-year.%20The%20gains%20were%20partly%20driven%20by%20its%20%26quot%3BHealthcare%20and%20Others%26quot%3B%20segment%20which%20includes%20electronic%20materials%20used%20in%20semiconductors%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20February%20earnings%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Ajinomoto%20posted%20its%20earnings%20on%20February%205%2C%20the%20company's%20stock%20rose%2013%25.%20Its%20shares%20are%20up%20more%20than%2056%25%20over%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20non-tech%20companies%20are%20benefiting%20equally%20from%20the%20AI%20boom.%20Daikin%2C%20best%20known%20globally%20for%20its%20air%20conditioners%2C%20supplies%20high-purity%20chemical%20materials%20used%20in%20semiconductor%20manufacturing.%20It%20recently%20trimmed%20its%20outlook%2C%20citing%20uncertainty%20over%20US%20tariffs%20as%20a%20drag%20on%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Japanese%20air%20conditioning%20maker%20reduced%20its%20operating%20profit%20forecast%20by%20about%205%25%20to%20413%20billion%20Japanese%20yen%2C%20or%20%242.6%20billion%2C%20for%20the%20fiscal%20year%20ending%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOperating%20profit%20was%20significantly%20affected%20by%20the%20decline%20in%20semiconductor%20demand%2C%20decreasing%20by%2044.6%25%20year%20over%20year%20to%20%C2%A518%2C102%20million%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20its%20financial%20report%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNet%20sales%20of%20fluoropolymers%20fell%20year%20over%20year%2C%20despite%20focused%20Group%20efforts%20to%20capture%20strong%20new%20demand%20in%20the%20data%20center%20field%2C%20and%20was%20due%20to%20the%20stagnation%20in%20the%20construction%20markets%20of%20the%20United%20States%20and%20China%20and%20the%20significant%20overall%20impact%20of%20delays%20in%20the%20recovery%20of%20semiconductor%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20cushion%20the%20blow%20through%20price%20increases%20and%20cost%20reductions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaikin's%20stock%20dropped%20as%20much%20as%208.4%25%20in%20Tokyo%20following%20its%20financial%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoilet-toto-seasoning-food-ajinomoto-japan-winners-ai-boom-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771575748000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69981bb4e1ba468a96ac5ddc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoilet-toto-seasoning-food-ajinomoto-japan-winners-ai-boom-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20AI%20surge%20is%20lifting%20companies%20in%20the%20semiconductor%20supply%20chain%20%E2%80%94%20including%20a%20toilet%20maker%20and%20a%20seasoning%20giant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cmlee%40insider.com%20(Lee%20Chong%20Ming)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoilet-toto-seasoning-food-ajinomoto-japan-winners-ai-boom-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'KHxRK'%20promo%3A%20Kamal%20Haasan%20and%20Rajinikanth%20in%20one%20frame%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771575516000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-128599397%2Cimgsize-63064.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fkhxrk-kamal-haasan-and-rajinikanth-in-one-frame-fresh-poster-hints-the-promo-update%2Farticleshow%2F128599397.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F128599397.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ETamil%20cinema%20is%20buzzing%20as%20legends%20Kamal%20Haasan%20and%20Rajinikanth%20unite%20after%2045%20years.%20A%20new%20poster%2C%20featuring%20symbolic%20hands%2C%20hints%20at%20a%20promo%20update%20on%20February%2021st%20at%2012%3A07%20PM%2C%20a%20time%20paying%20tribute%20to%20their%20birthd