20the%20past%20year%2C%20hitting%20a%20record%20high%20above%20%245%2C500%20per%20ounce%20late%20last%20month%20before%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-price-silver-price-today-market-crash-outlook-forecast-warsh-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esharp%20correction.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20gold's%20rise%20has%20been%20buoyed%20by%20central%20bank%20buying%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20sharp%20price%20swings%20have%20temporarily%20slowed%20that%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20conversations%20suggest%20that%20reserve%20managers%20remain%20willing%20buyers%20of%20gold%20to%20hedge%20geopolitical%20and%20financial%20risks%20but%20prefer%20to%20delay%20purchases%20until%20prices%20stabilize%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman%20commodity%20analysts%20Lina%20Thomas%20and%20Daan%20Struyven%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20elevated%20volatility%20was%20driven%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-price-today-rebound-5000-dip-buying-forecast-outlook-silver-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprivate-sector%20diversification%20demand%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20much%20of%20it%20expressed%20through%20gold%20call-option%20structures%20that%20amplify%20price%20moves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20volatility%20has%20made%20some%20emerging-market%20central%20banks%20more%20hesitant%20to%20step%20in%20aggressively%20at%20current%20levels%2C%20even%20as%20they%20remain%20structurally%20bullish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECentral%20banks%20bought%20roughly%201%2C000%20metric%20tons%20of%20gold%20on%20a%20net%20basis%20in%202023%20and%202024%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Gold%20Council.%20That%20dipped%20to%20around%20900%20tons%20in%202025%2C%20but%20they%20bought%20at%20higher%20prices%20compared%20to%20the%20past%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Fgold-price%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpot%20gold%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20trading%20around%20%244%2C995%20per%20troy%20ounce%20in%20early%20Friday%20trade.%20Prices%20are%20up%20about%2016%25%20so%20far%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d56d9219-e33d-4005-81c8-dd67e1b9bece%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EVolatility%20masks%20steady%20demand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20structural%20backdrop%2C%20Goldman's%20analysts%20argued%2C%20hasn't%20changed.%20Since%20the%20freezing%20of%20Russia's%20reserves%20over%20its%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20in%202022%2C%20central%20banks%20have%20reassessed%20the%20risks%20of%20holding%20dollar%20assets%20and%20started%20buying%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-price-today-5000-government-bonds-debt-warning-treasurys-jgb-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egold%20as%20an%20alternative.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20base%20case%20%E2%80%94%20which%20assumes%20no%20additional%20surge%20in%20private-sector%20diversification%20%E2%80%94%20Goldman%20expects%20volatility%20to%20moderate%20and%20central-bank%20buying%20to%20reaccelerate%2C%20broadly%20in%20line%20with%20the%20pace%20seen%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETogether%20with%20incremental%20private-investor%20demand%20tied%20to%20potential%20Federal%20Reserve%20rate%20cuts%2C%20that%20could%20push%20gold%20to%20%245%2C400%20an%20ounce%20by%20the%20end%20of%202026%2C%20the%20bank%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20diversification%20demand%20accelerates%20further%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20on%20concerns%20about%20fiscal%20risks%20in%20Western%20economies%20%E2%80%94%20volatility%20could%20remain%20elevated.%20That's%20especially%20true%20if%20the%20flows%20continue%20to%20be%20expressed%20through%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20case%2C%20near-term%20central-bank%20demand%20may%20be%20dampened%20even%20as%20prices%20rise%20more%20sharply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Miller%2C%20the%20chief%20investment%20officer%20of%20%2410%20billion%20Catalyst%20Funds%2C%20echoed%20the%20longer-term%20case%20for%20official-sector%20demand%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20mining%20perspective%2C%20there%20has%20been%20some%20selling%20by%20individuals%20cashing%20in%20their%20gold%20holdings%20at%20higher%20prices%2C%20but%20nothing%20on%20a%20scale%20that%20could%20offset%20the%201%2C000%20metric%20tons%20of%20net%20buying%20by%20central%20banks%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiller%2C%20who%20manages%20a%20gold%20ETF%2C%20added%20that%20central%20banks%20are%20likely%20to%20continue%20buying%20gold%2C%20keeping%20demand%20ahead%20of%20supply%2C%20as%20mining%20output%20can't%20be%20ramped%20up%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20appears%20we're%20transitioning%20back%20into%20a%20longer-term%20rally%2C%20though%20one%20that%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20much%20choppier%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-price-today-central-banks-buying-outlook-goldman-sachs-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1771566737000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6997c8c5e1ba468a96ac5c8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-price-today-central-banks-buying-outlook-goldman-sachs-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gold's%20volatility%20has%20pushed%20central%20banks%20to%20the%20sidelines%2C%20despite%20their%20long-term%20bullish%20stance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-price-today-central-banks-buying-outlook-goldman-sachs-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ambulance%20stuck%20in%20traffic%20jam%20as%20youths%20cut%20cake%2C%20burst%20crackers%20on%20highway%20for%20birthday%20bash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%2