2%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6997d834f8731049f3af742d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222995%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlien%20prediction%20markets%20are%20heating%20up%20as%20Trump%20vows%20to%20release%20secret%20UFO%20files.%3Cp%3EChip%20Somodevilla%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20says%20he%20is%20going%20to%20declassify%20files%20about%20aliens%20and%20UFOs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20could%20mean%20huge%20payouts%20for%20traders%20betting%20on%20alien%20disclosure%20on%20the%20prediction%20platform%20Polymarket.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAliens%20have%20long%20occupied%20a%20strange%20but%20persistent%20corner%20of%20the%20betting%20world.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20says%20he%20is%20directing%20federal%20agencies%20to%20declassify%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fufo-sightings-ratcliffe-new-report-intel-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUFO%20files%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20traders%20betting%20on%20aliens%2C%20that%20could%20mean%20a%20very%20earthly%20payday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20the%20tremendous%20interest%20shown%2C%20I%20will%20be%20directing%20the%20Secretary%20of%20War%2C%20and%20other%20relevant%20Departments%20and%20Agencies%2C%20to%20begin%20the%20process%20of%20identifying%20and%20releasing%20Government%20files%20related%20to%20alien%20and%20extraterrestrial%20life%2C%20unidentified%20aerial%20phenomena%20(UAP)%2C%20and%20unidentified%20flying%20objects%20(UFOs)%2C%20and%20any%20and%20all%20other%20information%20connected%20to%20these%20highly%20complex%2C%20but%20extremely%20interesting%20and%20important%2C%20matters%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%20on%20Thursday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Trump%20took%20aim%20at%20former%20President%20Barack%20Obama%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20improperly%20discussing%20classified%20material%20when%20speaking%20about%20extraterrestrial%20life%20on%20a%20recent%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20told%20reporters%20aboard%20Air%20Force%20One%20that%20Obama%20%26quot%3Bgave%20classified%20information%26quot%3B%20and%20wasn't%20%26quot%3Bsupposed%20to%20be%20doing%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20he%20could%20get%20him%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20trouble%26quot%3B%20by%20declassifying%20the%20relevant%20files.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObama%20said%20in%20a%20tongue-in-cheek%20exchange%20with%20podcaster%20Brian%20Tyler%20Cohen%20last%20week%20that%20aliens%20are%20%26quot%3Breal%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20they're%20not%20%26quot%3Bbeing%20kept%26quot%3B%20at%20Area%2051.%20He%20later%20clarified%20in%20an%20Instagram%20post%20that%20there%20was%20no%20evidence%20during%20his%20presidency%20that%20aliens%20%26quot%3Bhave%20made%20contact%20with%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAliens%20have%20always%20had%20a%20niche%20following.%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-political-fight-over-prediction-markets-is-heating-up-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprediction%20markets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20aliens%20are%20tradable%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20decentralized%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fethereum-creator-polymarket-backer-raises-concern-about-prediction-markets-future-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprediction%20platform%20Polymarket%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20guessing%20about%20aliens%20has%20become%20a%20high-volume%20betting%20category.%20Traders%20have%20poured%20millions%20of%20dollars%20into%20whether%20the%20US%20will%20confirm%20the%20existence%20of%20extraterrestrial%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20platform's%20largest%20markets%20asks%20whether%20the%20US%20will%20confirm%20that%20aliens%20exist%20before%202027.%20The%20market%20has%20drawn%20more%20than%20%244%20million%20in%20trading%20volume%20as%20of%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetting%20activity%20has%20also%20centered%20on%20whether%20a%20Trump%20administration%20would%20declassify%20UFO%20files%20before%202027%2C%20with%20odds%20climbing%20above%2080%25%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolymarket%20users%20also%20placed%20bets%20on%20other%20extraterrestrial%20theories%2C%20including%20whether%20mysterious%20drones%20spotted%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-we-know-about-mysterious-drones-new-jersey-new-york-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20Jersey%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20aliens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20files%20are%20released%20and%20contain%20anything%20definitive%2C%20longtime%20alien%20bettors%20may%20finally%20cash%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b3806380-524a-487f-8818-f8871009e6ee%5C%22%3ENotable%20speculation%20about%20aliens%20and%20UFOs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202024%2C%20unidentified%20drones%20were%20seen%20flying%20at%20night%20over%20New%20Jersey%20and%20other%20East%20Coast%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrones-new-jersey-online-mystery-conspiracy-why-explained-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emysterious%20sightings%3C%2Fa%3E%20unsettled%20residents%20and%20drew%20questions%20from%20local%20officials%2C%20fueling%20a%20wave%20of%20speculation%20about%20what%20%E2%80%94%20or%20who%20%E2%80%94%20was%20in%20the%20sky.%20Alien%20theories%20quickly%20gained%20traction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20Trump%20said%20the%20government%20%26quot%3Bknows%20what%20is%20happening%26quot%3B%20but%20wasn't%20sharing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20some%20reason%2C%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20comment.%20I%20think%20they'd%20be%20better%20off%20saying%20what%20it%20is.%20Our%20military%20knows%2C%20and%20our%20president%20knows%2C%20and%20for%20some%20reason%2C%20they%20want%20to%20keep%20people%20in%20suspense%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20Mar-a-Lago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomething%20strange%20is%20going%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3